Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "node_end_good", "exploration_depth": "surface"}], "is_endpoint": false, "endpoint_type": null}, "node_5k": {"id": "node_5k", "persona_text": "I never thought about it that way. Handling escalations really does involve similar skills. And I''m good at it - I usually resolve things calmly.", "persona_mood": "neutral_uncertain", "themes": ["Goals", "Change"], "choice_points": [{"id": "cp_node_5k_0", "option_text": "You''re seeing the connection between skills you already use successfully and what would be needed in leadership. That''s building your confidence that you have relevant abilities.", "preview_hint": "MI-consistent approach", "rapport_impact": 1, "resistance_impact": -1, "tone_shift": 0.15, "technique_tags": ["complex_reflection"], "competency_links": ["B6"], "feedback": {"immediate": "Excellent! This reflects their growing Ability change talk and confidence.", "learning_note": "Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "node_end_good", "exploration_depth": "surface"}], "is_endpoint": false, "endpoint_type": null}, "node_5l": {"id": "node_5l", "persona_text": "That makes me feel more confident actually. I do have relevant skills. Maybe the gap isn''t as big as I thought.", "persona_mood": "neutral_uncertain", "themes": ["Goals", "Change"], "choice_points": [{"id": "cp_node_5l_0", "option_text": "Your confidence is growing as you recognize the skills you already have. The transition to leadership feels more achievable than you initially thought.", "preview_hint": "MI-consistent approach", "rapport_impact": 1, "resistance_impact": -1, "tone_shift": 0.15, "technique_tags": ["complex_reflection"], "competency_links": ["B6"], "feedback": {"immediate": "Perfect! This reflects their emerging Activation change talk - the shift in how they view the possibility.", "learning_note": "Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "node_end_good", "exploration_depth": "surface"}], "is_endpoint": false, "endpoint_type": null}, "node_5m": {"id": "node_5m", "persona_text": "Well, that''s discouraging. I thought I was making connections, but maybe I''m overestimating myself.", "persona_mood": "disappointed_closed", "themes": ["General"], "choice_points": [{"id": "cp_node_5m_0", "option_text": "I didn''t mean to discourage you. The skills are relevant - they''re just not identical. Your listening and calm under pressure would absolutely help in performance conversations.", "preview_hint": "MI-consistent approach", "rapport_impact": 0, "resistance_impact": 0, "tone_shift": 0.0, "technique_tags": ["unknown"], "competency_links": [], "feedback": {"immediate": "Good recovery - you take responsibility and affirm the Ability change they expressed.", "learning_note": "Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "node_end_moderate", "exploration_depth": "surface"}], "is_endpoint": false, "endpoint_type": null}, "node_5n": {"id": "node_5n", "persona_text": "I think timing is big. And whether I want to commit to something bigger when my personal life is demanding. But also... I don''t want to stay in my current role forever. I need to grow.", "persona_mood": "neutral_uncertain", "themes": ["Goals", "Barriers", "Change"], "choice_points": [{"id": "cp_node_5n_0", "option_text": "So there''s tension between wanting to grow and the demands of your personal life right now. Both are real considerations for you.", "preview_hint": "MI-consistent approach", "rapport_impact": 1, "resistance_impact": -1, "tone_shift": 0.15, "technique_tags": ["double_sided_reflection"], "competency_links": ["B6"], "feedback": {"immediate": "Excellent! This reflects both their Desire for growth AND their legitimate concern about timing.", "learning_note": "Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "node_end_good", "exploration_depth":